{"tid":1786392,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"點解運動好似愈嚟愈少人？因為唔夠宣傳啊！","createTime":"2019-12-17T06:09:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T11:38:40.000Z","uid":89974,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"22e92209c0004b9d9db52fcce9ec84321a065252","tid":1786392,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:09:28.000Z","msg":"幾個月前有位手足做咗幾張好清晰嘅文宣，我一直save低咗係電腦，就係知道人類總會重覆犯錯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記住時刻提醒自己<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌係無撚用</span></span><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">，行動最實際</span></span><br />\n唔夠人行動除咗好多人變番港豬嘅可能性之外，更加有可能係我地根本做唔夠宣傳！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">宣傳係人都做得，所以唔夠人行動係所有人嘅責任</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同樣道理，核心抗爭分子係唔可以灰心，因為我地先係運動入面最重要個一群，200萬人入面有絕大部份人都係等緊人去lead，而呢場戰爭嘅勝負就係取決於我地核心群同政府嘅<span style=\"color: purple;\">動員能力</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雨革最大失敗嘅影響係絕大部份人因為太多分化，無目標，捉鬼而心灰意冷，導致出現長達5年嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>政府冷感期</strong></span>。但今次再輸，我地就唔會再有政府冷感期，而係人肉保鮮期<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kbcxCxX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkbcxCxX.png&h=26715f44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GGH5XxY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGGH5XxY.png&h=082a1fc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係連儂牆風險愈嚟愈高嘅時候，除咗連登，Telegram，唔好唔記得Facebook同Whatsapp先係最多人用！<br />\n1.捕實所有大新聞page(蘋果，立場，等等)，一見佢地出post即刻留言宣傳最近活動！<br />\n2.每日發1張行動文宣俾3位你識嘅黃絲朋友，再呼籲佢地發出去！<br />\n3.Airdrop宣傳<br />\n4.袋定幾張文宣，行行下間唔中就當街招咁貼一張文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />降低連儂牆手足中伏嘅風險！<br />\n5.之前手足教咗街招大法，低風險又高傷害但都無乜人做<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1777171/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1777171/page/1</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>吹水最無謂，行動最實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"8e82e54767c4d4d8fcd64b7bff3be43ff261f8ba","tid":1786392,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:09:44.000Z","msg":"香港金總終於接受網上會員申請啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786114</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3d032e40a30bdb3b0e872e4c7abacad729e9b344","tid":1786392,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:09:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb4c4c87b30e8b45e409cda197b9205692ddc319","tid":1786392,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e82e54767c4d4d8fcd64b7bff3be43ff261f8ba","tid":1786392,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:09:44.000Z","msg":"香港金總終於接受網上會員申請啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786114</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7608af7c23eaa44a7ed9922d3fdd79d52eb777","tid":1786392,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:10:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34842013e620d8b486096f538fefb19b4a207b62","tid":1786392,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply